{"tid":546021,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【13:59更新】地盤附近的新鴻基中心商戶及寫字樓員工須疏散","createTime":"2018-01-31T06:08:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-31T06:28:05.000Z","uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b9aa787f39e385bb118dc403f01014727ea2313c","tid":546021,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T06:08:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180131/57775165\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180131%2F57775165&d=avymZ6sZwhxXJiMoodLcDcPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=c48e227c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180131%2F57775165&h=4b3f4d23\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180131/57775165</a><br />\n<br />\n【13:59更新】地盤附近的新鴻基中心商戶及寫字樓員工須疏散<br />\n<br />\n【13:15更新】運輸署宣佈，因發現炸彈，灣仔北的主要道路已經陸續封閉。預計灣仔北一帶交通將會十分擠塞<br />\n【13:09更新】灣仔運動場正舉行學界田徑賽，有40多間中學參與，一眾師生被警方通知須疏散到安全地方，田徑賽活動取消。<br />\n早上11時15分，灣仔會議道與杜老誌道交界沙中綫地盤，工人工作期間發現懷疑戰時炸彈，警方接報趕至調查，爆炸品處理課亦將奉召到場處理，稍後封鎖有關路段戒備。<br />\n運輸署於下午1時宣佈：因發現炸彈，灣仔北的主要道路已經陸續封閉。預計灣仔北一帶交通將會十分擠塞，駕駛人士請避免駕駛前往灣仔北。<br />\n地盤附近的新鴻基中心，商戶及寫字樓，亦受炸彈事件影響而須封閉，員工已陸續疏散離開新鴻基中心。<br />\n剛過去的周六(27號)灣仔沙中綫地盤發現二戰炮彈(<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2DEjB1q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2DEjB1q&d=avymZ6sZwhxXJiMoodLcDcPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=c1a4eba1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2DEjB1q</a>)，為1000磅美式AN-M65炮彈，計及疏散及封路等時間，由發現炮彈到成功拆除，警方共花了25-26個小時。"},{"pid":"61b61f501cc13c31cbaeff55257e1c433314c97c","tid":546021,"uid":12568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9aa787f39e385bb118dc403f01014727ea2313c","tid":546021,